raw_data.title: HE Analyst I
raw_data.description: Under supervision, performs basic analysis of systems, operations, or processes utilizing basic, known tools and techniques. Areas of support can include engineering, testing, training, acquisition, financial, cost, and/or training support. Performs tasks that are routine and learns to apply training to practice. May perform other duties as required.

raw_data.title: HE Analyst II

Works within defined guidelines. May perform other duties as required.

raw_data.title: HE Analyst III

raw_data.title: HE Analyst IV
raw_data.description: Performs analysis of systems, operations, or processes utilizing advanced tools and techniques. raw_data.title: HE Analyst V
